articles.title: Australian Open 2023: Priyanshu Rajawat breezes past Srikanth, Prannoy stuns World No. 2, Sindhu out - Khel Now
articles.description: Young Priyanshu Rajawat beat Kidambi Srikanth, while HS Prannoy went past Anthony Ginting to set up an all-Indian semi-final clash in Australian Open 2023.
articles.content: Indias top ranked shuttler HS Prannoy and young Priyanshu Rajawat won their respective quarter-finals matches to set-up an all-Indian mens singles semi-final clash in Australian Open 2023. Priyanshu,… [+2658 chars]
